Flocks of migratory birds were spotted foraging and relaxing on wetlands in northwest China's Qinghai Province on their journey to the north.Qianzi Lake is a gathering spot for various kinds of migratory birds including the greater white-fronted goose, grey goose and bar-headed goose. (Cover image via VCG) (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)